merchant.name: Tiong Shian Porridge Centre - New Bridge Road
merchant.description:
This popular food stall sells many different ypes of porridge and claypot dishes, with some other simple zi char dishes on the side. Try the fish or fish head porridge, claypot frog porridge or pork liver porridge, with a serving of raw fish on the side. 
Source: hungrygowhere.com
